title: mvid-dvdrip.x264.mp3.vol3-TRiPTEC
description:
It's been a while, did the encoding sometime ago. The videoencoding is the same as the other packs, but now I'm using mp3 for audio. When I did those i used avi as container, newer is going to be mp4 I think. Well please comment, it makes it more fun. But I make this mainly for my self as I don't like the full dvd's they usually  are released in. Some of them aren't great, mainly because of the source, but hey, there is allways room for improvement. So if you got any tips please pm me or just comment. I use mplayer/mencoder. 

Enjoy!
//triptec
